<br>
I don't think so, something with the data I don't understand.<br>
<br>
You show the Enchanter chain casting with 0 recast time, but two spells with 6 sec casting time and 8 sec recast cannot be chain cast. There will be a delay.<br>
<br>
Also, regarding the Gather Mana ability. You gave the Enchanters 1/2 the mana from the ability, assuming a fight every 1/2 hour. Refresh on Gather Mana is just shy of 2.5 hours. It would seem to me that they should be given 1/5 of the mana, not 1/2.  <p><BR>
